title: USC Leventhal MAcc & MBT Info Sessions
desc: Please join us for an info session to learn more about our Master of Accounting and Master of Business Taxation programs. This will be a great opportunity to ask questions, hear experiences from our current students and meet the Leventhal admissions team.? Parking: We recommend parking in Parking Structure 2 (Exposition Parking Structure) located right behind the Radisson Mid-City Hotel at: 3335 South Flower Street Los Angeles, CA 90089 ?Please enter the structure off of Figueroa Street and keep an eye out for the Parking Structure 2 (PS2) sign. A daily parking pass is $12 and can be purchased with the parking lot attendant. Please allow 15 minutes to park your car and walk to Leventhal (ACC), locatedon the campus map.
